race.description: Brown Family Wine Group Maiden Handicap
race.comment: UPSTART LOVER (14) returned to racing with a solid third at Gatton over 1100m. She's further improved and has been kept on the fresh side. Will have come on and this is a winnable assignment. DARTH INVADER (1) has a wide gate to manage but rates a threat. Went forward last start and gave a great sight beaten 1L over 1050m. He'd switched from a Victorian yard on a 33-day return and still has more to give. PRINCE OF SYNERGY (4) is a former Victorian having his first run for the Sharon Croxford yard. Hasn't been seen at the trials but he has pieces of form that would see him very competitive. Has an outside gate but has to be kept safe. ATHOL MAC (6) returned last time here and looked a run short. This looks a bit harder, but he maps well and the 2kg claim is handy. DESTINY GUNGHO (7) has race fitness and may be the best of the remaining runners.
